channel.description: I just finished buying a vps fom vpsland.com how do i use it with my mopar ip? please answer!

item.title: I just finished getting vps from vpsland.com how i use it with my ip?
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

I believe your “mopar ip” is your DNS redirect rsscapev4.no-ip.biz, therefore you need to go onto no-ip.com and need to edit the address and change the IP to the one that your vps provided (normally in an email)
